#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.27:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Pañcaṅgikavagga "
msgstr "3. With Five Factors "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Samādhisutta "
msgstr "27. Immersion "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.27:1.1"
msgid "“Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvetha appamāṇaṃ nipakā patissatā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, develop limitless immersion, alert and mindful. "

msgctxt "an5.27:1.2"
msgid "Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvayataṃ appamāṇaṃ nipakānaṃ patissatānaṃ pañca ñāṇāni paccattaññeva uppajjanti. "
msgstr "When you develop limitless immersion, alert and mindful, five knowledges arise for you personally. "

msgctxt "an5.27:1.3"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.27:1.4"
msgid "‘Ayaṃ samādhi paccuppannasukho ceva āyatiñca sukhavipāko’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ uppajjati, "
msgstr "‘This immersion is blissful now, and results in bliss in the future.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.27:1.5"
msgid "‘ayaṃ samādhi ariyo nirāmiso’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ uppajjati, "
msgstr "‘This immersion is noble and spiritual.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: akāpurisasevito’ti → mahāpurisasevitoti (mr)
msgctxt "an5.27:1.6"
msgid "‘ayaṃ samādhi akāpurisasevito’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ uppajjati, "
msgstr "‘This immersion is not cultivated by sinners.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: na sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato’ti → na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritacatoti (bj) | na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritappattoti (s1-3) | na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritāvaṭoti (pts1) | na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavārivāvaṭoti (mr) | na sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāriyādhigatoti (?)
msgctxt "an5.27:1.7"
msgid "‘ayaṃ samādhi santo paṇīto paṭippassaddhaladdho ekodibhāvādhigato, na sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ uppajjati, "
msgstr "‘This immersion is peaceful and sublime and tranquil and unified, not held in place by forceful suppression.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: sato vuṭṭhahāmī’ti → sato ca uṭṭhahāmīti (bj) | sato vuṭṭhahāmīti (s1-3, km) | so kho panāhaṃ imaṃ samādhiṃ satova samāpajjāmi satova vuṭṭhahāmīti (pts1)
msgctxt "an5.27:1.8"
msgid "‘sato kho panāhaṃ imaṃ samāpajjāmi sato vuṭṭhahāmī’ti paccattaññeva ñāṇaṃ uppajjati. "
msgstr "‘I mindfully enter into and emerge from this immersion.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.27:2.1"
msgid "Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvetha appamāṇaṃ nipakā patissatā. "
msgstr "Develop limitless immersion, alert and mindful. "

msgctxt "an5.27:2.2"
msgid "Samādhiṃ, bhikkhave, bhāvayataṃ appamāṇaṃ nipakānaṃ patissatānaṃ imāni pañca ñāṇāni paccattaññeva uppajjantī”ti. "
msgstr "When you develop limitless immersion, alert and mindful, these five knowledges arise for you personally.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.27:2.3"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
